                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Uh... why not just ping pong the aggro in the mid levels?<br /><br />Pet taunt off,<br /><br />Pull with snare and dots, get high aggro.<br />Fear and sic pet on.<br />Sit and med until fear wears off<br />Keep sitting and medding while mob still has aggro and is walking back to you<br />Refear, redot, resnare, whatever needs refresh<br /><br />Rinse repeat... easist way to keep mana up and still kill fast<br /><br />As far as the planes go, its all about aggrokiting anyhow, most mobs dont flee there, so really, you dont, or cant, wait for those last 10-15%... and whats the point?<br /><br />Kill it, use the extra dmg from your Lifetap or Lifedrains to kill off the next mob and to keep him aggroed on your own arse<br /><br />Nuff said!</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
